      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTREME BLUE (2) was a fast winner last time with a dominant 10 lengths win (22.82) at this track. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. JUST ADD WATER (8) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 1.3 lengths into third (23.10) at Gosford in a Grade 5 over 388m. Expected to be in this for a long way. MIDNIGHT MOHAWK (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Early Concrete (23.62) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Will give a great sight again. KENNY'S GIRL (4) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
